# Pem backend (`backend/`)

**Package:** NestJS app under **`backend/`** — `npm install`, `npm run start:dev`, `npm run build` from `backend/`. No shared runtime code with `app/`.

**Stack:** **NestJS** ~11, **Drizzle ORM** + **`pg`**, **pgvector** (vector similarity search), **Clerk** JWT (**`jose`** + JWKS), **Svix** for `POST /webhooks/clerk`, **`@nestjs/throttler`**, **`@nestjs/swagger`** (`/docs` when not prod), **`ValidationPipe`**. **Config** — **`src/config/configuration.ts`**. **OpenAI** via **Vercel AI SDK v6** (`generateText` + `Output`, `embed`, never `generateObject`). **Background work** lives under **`src/background/`**. **Expo** push — **`notifyInboxUpdated`**. OpenAI **Whisper API** for voice transcription.

**Tables (Drizzle: `src/database/schemas/`):** **`users`** (incl. **`timezone`** IANA, **`notification_time`** for morning brief), **`messages`** (**`role`**: `user` | `pem`, **`kind`**: `text` | `voice` | `brief`, content, voice_url, transcript, **`triage_category`**, **`processing_status`**, polished_text, parent_message_id), **`message_embeddings`** (pgvector 1536-dim, FK to messages), **`extracts`** (tone, **urgency** `'someday'|'none'` — all timing via `period_start`/`period_end`/`due_at`, **`meta`** jsonb for rarely-queried fields, batch_key, status; **`message_id`** FK to messages; calendar event fields), **`calendar_connections`**, **`reported_issues`**, **`logs`** (unified audit: types include `chat`), **`memory_facts`**.

**Chat pipeline (workflow-style agent):** User sends message → `POST /chat/messages` → save → enqueue BullMQ `chat` job → return immediately (no AI on the HTTP path; triage runs in the worker).

`ChatOrchestratorService` processes:
1. **Transcribe** (voice messages via Whisper)
2. **Triage** (`TriageService`, gpt-4o-mini, routing-only) → `trivial` | `question_only` | `off_topic` | `needs_agent`
3. **Route:**
   - `trivial` → quick acknowledgment
   - `off_topic` → short redirect (weather, trivia, general knowledge — Pem does not engage)
   - `question_only` → `ChatQuestionService` (RAG + extracts + memory + gpt-4o; only *their* data)
   - `needs_agent` → **`PemAgentService`** — **prompt chaining** (Anthropic-style workflow): (1) **extraction** pass → `creates` / `updates` / `completions` only, low temperature, retries + JSON recovery; (2) **orchestration** pass → `response_text`, calendar, memory, scheduling, etc., using locked extraction JSON in the prompt; if orchestration fails, **synthesized** reply from extraction counts; if extraction stays empty but heuristics say the message is actionable, **monolithic** single-call fallback (full schema, same retries + recovery as before)
   - **Context to the agent:** open tasks (inbox/snoozed), upcoming timed items from those tasks, **today’s** timed subset, **done** extracts (last 90 days), **dismissed** extracts (last 30 days, to avoid re-extracting), last **30** chat messages (chronological), memory facts, scheduling slots/prefs, **RAG** lines (similarity ≥ **0.75**, top **10** — query embedded after message is saved). **Programmatic dedupe:** new `creates` that match an open or recently dismissed task (normalized, case-insensitive) are dropped before DB apply.
4. **Apply** agent output: creates, updates, completions, calendar_writes, memory_writes
5. **Respond** — save Pem response message, publish via SSE, push notification
6. **Embed** chat lines into pgvector (background): **user** messages after successful handling; **Pem** replies when saved. **Idempotent** per `message_id` (unique index). Stored text is `[ISO] user:|pem: …` for RAG clarity.

**SSE:** `GET /chat/stream` — `X-Accel-Buffering: no`, **heartbeat** every **30s** (type `heartbeat`), events: `status`, `pem_message`, `message_updated`, `processing_failed` (final job failure). Redis pub/sub via `ChatEventsService` (`chat-events:{userId}`).

**Chat idempotency & jobs:** `POST /chat/messages` optional **`idempotency_key`** (unique per user) returns the existing message if replayed. BullMQ job id **`chat-msg:{messageId}`** dedupes duplicate enqueue. Worker **attempts: 3**, exponential backoff; logs **messageId** only (no user text). Pipeline skips work if `processing_status` is already **`done`**.

**Morning brief:** `BriefCronService` — hourly cron checks user timezones, generates brief at midnight (user local), saves as `kind: 'brief'` Pem message, delayed push at user's `notification_time`.

**Calendar integration:** Google Calendar only (server-side OAuth + API via `googleapis`). Agent can emit `calendar_writes` to create events. OAuth `state` is **HMAC-signed** with env **`GOOGLE_OAUTH_STATE_SECRET`** (required whenever `GET /calendar/google/auth-url` is used); callback verifies signature + expiry before `upsertGoogle`.

**AI models:** `gpt-4o-mini` for triage. `gpt-4o` for PemAgent, question answering, morning brief. `text-embedding-3-small` for pgvector embeddings. `whisper-1` for voice.

**API:**

```
POST /chat/messages     ← send message (text, voice, or image with `image_key` / optional `content` caption)
POST /chat/photos/upload-url ← presigned PUT to R2 for `chat-images/{userId}/{uuid}.ext`; client PUTs then POSTs message with `kind: image`
GET  /chat/messages     ← paginated history (?before=ISO&limit=50); image rows include signed `image_urls` when R2 is configured
GET  /chat/stream       ← SSE (one per user session)

GET  /extracts/done|open|query|:id|:id/history
POST /extracts/:id/draft
PATCH /extracts/:id/done|dismiss|undone|undismiss|snooze|reschedule
PATCH /extracts/:id — user edit (partial JSON: text, urgency `someday|none`, batch_key, due_at, period_start, period_end, period_label, duration_minutes, pem_note, is_deadline, energy_level, tone; calendar-linked tasks reject schedule fields)
POST /extracts/:id/report

PATCH /users/me/timezone
GET  /calendar/connections
GET  /calendar/google/auth-url
GET  /calendar/google/callback
PATCH /calendar/connections/:id/primary
DELETE /calendar/connections/:id
```

**Layout:**

| Area | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/chat/` | `ChatModule` — controller, service, stream service. `POST /chat/messages`, `GET /chat/messages`, `GET /chat/stream` (SSE). |
| `src/agents/` | `AgentsModule` — `TriageService` (gpt-4o-mini), `PemAgentService` (gpt-4o: extraction + orchestration passes, monolithic fallback). |
| `src/embeddings/` | `EmbeddingsModule` — embed messages, similarity search via pgvector. |
| `src/background/queues/chat/` | BullMQ `chat` queue: `ChatProcessor`, `ChatOrchestratorService`, `ChatQuestionService`. |
| `src/background/queues/brief/` | `BriefCronService` — morning brief generation + push. |
| `src/background/queues/calendar/` | BullMQ `calendar-sync` queue: sync processor, cron. |
| `src/background/chat-events/` | Redis pub/sub — user-scoped channels for SSE. |
| `src/calendar/` | `CalendarModule` — connections CRUD, Google OAuth, sync. |
| `src/extracts/` | Extract CRUD, brief buckets, draft generation. |
| `src/users/` | User CRUD, timezone, push token. |
| `src/profile/` | `memory_facts` CRUD. |
| `src/push/` | Expo push. |
| `src/transcription/` | Whisper via OpenAI API. |
| `src/storage/` | R2 audio storage. |
| `src/auth/`, `src/webhooks/`, `src/health/` | unchanged. |

**Drizzle:** Change schema in TS → **`npm run db:generate`** → review → **`npm run db:migrate`**. Never hand-edit `drizzle/*.sql` or `drizzle/meta/`.

**Security:** Validate input; **`ClerkAuthGuard`** + DB user id from JWT. **CORS:** `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` must be a non-empty comma-separated list — bootstrap throws if missing (no wildcard / reflective fallback). **Prod:** **`OPENAI_API_KEY`** must be set or config load fails (fail-fast).

**Maintenance:** When **schema, routes, queues, or env** change, update **this file** in the same effort. See **`pem-project.mdc`**.
